The military swords are a bit heavier and with less finesse, 
but are more durable.

short sword    dam 5, abs 7,
1h             str 5 (max dam+1), finesse 4
               poke: mod-1 dam-1 pen+1 todefend-1
               swing: slow-1 mod-1 dam+1 todefend+2

broad sword    dam 7, abs 10,
1h             str 7 (max dam+2), finesse 4
               poke: mod-1 dam-1 pen+1 todefend-1
               swing: slow-1 mod-1 dam+2 todefend+2

long sword     dam 9, abs 13,
1h             str 9 (max dam+3), finesse 4
               poke: mod-1 dam-1 pen+1 todefend-1
               swing: slow-1 mod-1 dam+3 todefend+2

-

